sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant User as User
  participant SPFx as SPFx Web Part
  participant AAD as AadHttpClientFactory
  participant BFF as BFF (/chat/session)
  participant AES as Agent Execution Service
  participant MCP as MCP Protected API

  User->>SPFx: Open modern page
  SPFx->>AAD: getClient(bffResourceUri)
  AAD-->>SPFx: AadHttpClient (token managed by SPFx runtime)
  SPFx->>SPFx: Generate traceparent
  SPFx->>BFF: client.post('/chat/session', ...)<br/>headers: traceparent<br/>body: {display_name?}
  Note over SPFx,BFF: AadHttpClient adds Authorization header; web part never handles raw token
  Note over SPFx,BFF: userId/display_name is display-only context, never identity
  BFF->>BFF: Validate bearer token (identity source)
  BFF->>AES: Forward request + traceparent
  AES->>MCP: OBO call + traceparent
  MCP-->>AES: Response
  AES-->>BFF: Session payload
  BFF-->>SPFx: {session_id, expires_at}
  SPFx-->>User: Render session state
